### **MODE 2: Cartesian System Image**
```javascript
async function generateCartesianSystemImage(structureText, metadata) {
  // Extract unique clients and project types from metadata
  const yAxisLabels = [...new Set(metadata.clients)]; // e.g., ClientA, ClientB
  const xAxisLabels = [...new Set(metadata.projectTypes)]; // e.g., Invoice, Report

  const prompt = `
    Create an educational illustration showing a "Cartesian Coordinate System" 
    file organization labeled "(The New Way)".

    The image should show:
    - A confident stick figure with lightbulb (aha moment)
    - 3D isometric coordinate system with X, Y axes
    - Y-axis labeled "CLIENT" with values: ${yAxisLabels.join(', ')}
    - X-axis labeled "PROJECT TYPE" with values: ${xAxisLabels.join(', ')}
    - File icons at coordinate intersections

    Key visual elements:
