## 🔧 **Part 7: Technical Deep Dive**
![Code Mechanics](https://a.lovart.ai/artifacts/agent/M5rtG38I8j8PCOdD.png)

### **Environment Setup:**
```bash
# .env file
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Development server (with HMR)
npm run dev

# Production build
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview
```

### **API Integration Patterns:**

**Google Drive API Pattern:**
```javascript
// 1. Load API
await loadGoogleApi();

// 2. Initialize token client
const tokenClient = google.accounts.oauth2.initTokenClient({
  client_id: CLIENT_ID,
  scope: 'https://www.googleapis.com/auth/drive.readonly',
  callback: handleAuthResponse
});

// 3. Request access
tokenClient.requestAccessToken({ prompt: 'consent' });

// 4. Fetch data (recursive)
async function fetchDriveStructure(folderId, depth) {
  if (depth >= maxDepth) return;

  const response = await gapi.client.drive.files.list({
    q: `'${folderId}' in parents and trashed = false`,
    fields: 'files(id, name, mimeType, parents)',
    pageSize: 100
  });

  for (const file of response.result.files) {
    if (file.mimeType === 'application/vnd.google-apps.folder') {
      await fetchDriveStructure(file.id, depth + 1);
    }
  }
}
```

**Gemini AI API Pattern:**
```javascript
// 1. Load SDK
const { GoogleGenAI, Modality } = await loadGeminiSDK();

// 2. Initialize client
const ai = new GoogleGenAI({ apiKey: GEMINI_API_KEY });

// 3. Generate content
const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
  model: 'gemini-3-pro-image-preview',
  contents: prompt,
  config: {
    responseModalities: [Modality.TEXT, Modality.IMAGE],
    imageConfig: { aspectRatio: '16:9' }
  }
});

// 4. Extract image
const parts = response.candidates[0].content.parts;
const imageData = parts.find(p => p.inlineData);
const imageUrl = `data:${imageData.mimeType};base64,${imageData.data}`;
```

### **State Management Flow:**
```
IDLE → LOADING → SUCCESS → DISPLAY
  ↓         ↓
  ERROR ←---
```

### **Data Transformation Pipeline:**
```
Raw API Response
    ↓
Identify folders vs files
    ↓
Recursive structure building
    ↓
Nested tree structure
    ↓
Extract metadata (clients, types)
    ↓
Format for AI prompt
    ↓
Generate images
```

### **Performance Optimizations:**
✅ **Parallel API calls** - `Promise.all()` for both images  
✅ **Depth limiting** - `maxDepth = 4` prevents infinite recursion  
✅ **Page size optimization** - Fetch 100 items per request  
✅ **Error boundaries** - Graceful failure handling  
✅ **Dynamic script loading** - APIs load only when needed  

